{"tid":2432995,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"槍口下的良心》已至少19緬甸警察拒聽令開槍而逃至印度","createTime":"2021-03-04T16:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T00:48:32.000Z","uid":337052,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"291d681b8547a0bdd7afd1beba1fa4a7e863ad76","tid":2432995,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:20:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">緬甸警拒服從軍政府鎮壓令 已至少19人逃印度尋求庇護</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/04/phpvYI93j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F04%2FphpvYI93j.jpg&h=a65051f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n緬甸反政變示威行動越演越烈，軍警武力鎮壓手段也越來越血腥，但有不少「執法人員」無法接受上層指令。（歐新社）<br />\n<br />\n2021/03/05 00:01<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕緬甸反政變示威行動越演越烈，軍警武力鎮壓手段也越來越血腥，但有不少「執法人員」無法接受上層指令。<span class=\"red\">印度一名警官4日表示，至少有19名緬甸警察越境進入印度，躲避軍政府的命令。<br />\n</span><br />\n《路透》報導，由於事件敏感要求匿名的警官表示，這些人從東北部米佐拉姆邦（Mizoram）的邊境地區塞爾奇爾（Serchhip）和恰姆派（Champhai）進入印度，這2個與緬甸相連的地區邊境管理較鬆散。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，這些人都是基層警察，沒有武裝。該名警官還引述情報資料指出，「我們預期還會有更多人（逃到印度）」。<br />\n<br />\n根據社群媒體發布的內容，<span class=\"red\">參加反軍政府示威的群眾也包括緬甸警察，其中有一些人已被捕。</span><br />\n<br />\n這名警官表示，逃往印度的緬甸警察擔心違反上層指令而遭迫害，因此將被印度當地政府暫時安置。他說，「他們不想依指令對抗示威群眾」。<br />\n<br />\n另一名警官表示，這19名警察中，有3人是週三下午越過邊界靠近塞爾奇爾地區北凡萊拜鎮（North Vanlaiphai），當地政府正在評估他們的健康狀況。<br />\n<br />\n塞爾奇爾警察局長拉里納瑪（Stephen Lalrinawma）說，「他們表示，他們收到軍事統治者的指示，他們無法執行這些指示，所以逃離家園。他們尋求庇護，因為緬甸受到軍方統治」。<br />\n<br />\n印度與緬甸間有1600多公里陸上邊界。印度原本就已是成千上萬名緬甸難民的家園，包括羅興亞人和欽族人。<br />\n<br />\n但新德里的欽族社區負責人說，很少有警察逃到印度，「這很不尋常。在過去，警察和軍方只會遵從命令」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456764\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456764&d=Xhragic3nybqeCAZBODyv5a0YVntLK4LebkCjpCDSOM%3D&h=757c90f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456764&h=82a466af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456764</a>"},{"pid":"bf5fc869d6b801a28284963dae2ebdcfe556b5e8","tid":2432995,"uid":337052,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"槍口下港警有良心嗎？"},{"pid":"73ea459785dd1731d75e1e24b4ee14c445aaa6e8","tid":2432995,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:24:24.000Z","msg":"因為人工唔同囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcNETXr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcNETXr.jpg&h=78aad289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2280000/2283418/20190301_salary_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2280000%2F2283418%2F20190301_salary_1024.png&h=3dc6ff4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01508619f08e953c5c9df211e30fa08f6c26a8b5","tid":2432995,"uid":119478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:25:50.000Z","msg":"香港個班雨傘已經走左一大半啦"},{"pid":"c6f3e8717b0ae536c6a92435c28ba8c73d1fbd94","tid":2432995,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73ea459785dd1731d75e1e24b4ee14c445aaa6e8","tid":2432995,"uid":155095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T16:24:24.000Z","msg":"因為人工唔同囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qcNETXr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqcNETXr.jpg&h=78aad289&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2280000/2283418/20190301_salary_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2280000%2F2283418%2F20190301_salary_1024.png&h=3dc6ff4f&s={SIZE}\